{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world stands on the precipice of a revolution that will transform the landscape of the old world into a new realm of steel and smoky skies. Take control of a nation and guide it through this transformative time, embrace new technologies, and fight to survive and thrive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose Your Nation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as one of 84 countries spanning over 1000 provinces, each with unique starting situations from population and economics to diplomatic relations. You will need to forge alliances, build your army, and stabilize your country in order to overcome other adversaries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Grow Your Realm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help your people prosper by ensuring a stable flow of resources through domestic projects, buildings, and overseas expeditions. Conduct research on over 70 technologies inspired by the 19th and 20th centuries to unlock additional advancements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Compete for Global Dominance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight either at home or abroad among overseas areas to secure resources flowing to your country. Send armies overseas to capture territory or fortify your existing nation, improve your domain through development,  and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Clockwork Dawn is still early in development. Some features may be removed, changed, or added.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729302204","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953430/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729302204","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2953430/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729302204","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s